author: @jj.bbangtann5643
text:
Dear jin, 
I wanna start off by saying happy birthday!! I hope u had a great day! Have you eaten yet? Remember to sleep and eat wellğŸ’œ i just want to say thank you for everything u and bts has done for me in these past few months. Before i knew you guys, i was well depressed and had a lot of anxiety about schools and etc(i wont get into the details)  but anyways i just wanted to say a few words. I want to thank you for helping me get back on track with my life. The first song that i looked into was epiphany. I read the lyrics, listen closely to the tone, and i started feeling like i was not alone for once. It was hard for me to open up because i was scared. Now, im still pretty scared but i have improved just a little bit. I started to listen to all of bts's songs and realized that these lyrics arent JUST lyrics, they are something else. Something wonderful... something incredible. It was very hard to love myself. I looked in the mirror, and always hated what i saw. I started to compare myself to others. I started to cover myself up...hiding myself from the world. But you, you and bts, changed all that. Now i am no longer like that, although i get sad then and there, it does not affect me that much anymore. Your music helped me focus more on school and now instead of c's d's and f's, i got straight A's. I love you so much! I appriciate what u and what the rest of bts does to help others through music. I know it can be very tiring, but i know you can do it. I believe in you. You are KIM SEOKJIN after all. You are a part of BTS (The Most incredible, amazing, unpredicable, wonderful...ok sorry thats for another time heh) but what i was trying to say is, you are an incredible person. You just dont know how you and the rest of bangtan impacted my life. I will always be here to support you. If you feel like you are about to give up, look back at what you have done. Look at how much armys love you. You and bangtan deserves so much more love. Thank you so much for everything. I know that you dont know me but i know that you are here with me through your music. Thank you again. I love you. Dont forget to sleep and eat well, dont be too hard on yourself,and remember that bts and TRUE armys are right by your side. I have much more to say but thats for another time. I love you and have a wonderful birthday.

-your dearest fan, JDğŸ’œğŸ’œğŸ’œ

text:
Happy birthday to the Mr.World Wide Handsome. We, ARMY, appreciate how much you have contributed to BTS. Thank you for being strong for us through the tough times. Apologies for the times that you have felt left out or less than what you are at times. We want you to know you are so special. Bangtan Sonyedan is never complete without you! author: @jesuscristo2231
text:
[#HappyJinDay] Happy birthday Jin!
 I remember exactly the day I met you.  I remember his smile, his shyness, and his drawn eyes that smiled overflowing with happiness.  I barely knew then that I was about to meet someone so wonderful that it would change my life in some way.

 I didn't know your name, but I knew you were different, your eyes told me that.  You looked at the camera and showed such shyness, but over time that was changing.  You have grown, matured, become a man.  Strong, kind, zealous and friend.  Someone who has inspired me every day, someone who has filled a great void in me, and taught me never to give up, to persist voraciously in my dreams, for there is no big enough barrier that I cannot break.  Just as you did and have been doing.

 All of us (your true fans) have seen your efforts and your results.  Your vocal, your acting, your limb care, your dancing.  Yes, SeokJin!  Your dance!  Each year it becomes more noticeable that you have been trying your best - and beyond - to improve, but even if you can't do it all perfectly, the way you would like it, it doesn't matter!  Do you know why?  Because you are so much more than that.  Because your true achievement is your effort, your determination, your perseverance.  This is what makes you special, what makes you different.  It is your immense ability to love something so much that you can do nothing less than your best.  Even if it costs you a lot.

 How my heart hurts that on this special day I cannot be with you, give you a hug, thank you;  look into your eyes and tell you all that you mean to me.  But despite the distance, I hope you can feel all the good energies I send you.  All my affection, gratitude and, especially, all my love for you.

 Thank you for providing me with wonderful experiences and sharing your life with all of us.  I am grateful for your teaching, for all that has put me through.  Thank you for yesterday, where happiness was present.  I appreciate the night of rest, where sweet dreams reigned.  And it all just happened thanks to you.  Thank you for your words that brought me strength, peace, joy and happiness.  Strength to fight and overcome difficulties.  Joy for the simple pleasure of living.  Peace because you calmed my heart.  Happiness because only those who love are happy, and you have taught me to love again.

 May you be happy today and every other day of your life.  May your happiness only increase, more and more, and may the love of all the people who love you - truly - accompany this growth.

 Through this message, I want to thank you and congratulate you.  I want you to know everything you mean to me and how much has changed, not just my life, but that of many people.

 â€œI try to look into people's hearts, because we know that's where we get the best from us.â€

 Happy birthday Kim SeokJin.

i am not supposed to write a long letter saying how much i love him but for sure m gonna do that as for now i dont have my phone to tweet, insta or watch any live if there is.. it feels empty soo i wanna say here despite the fact who reads it or not. DEAR JINIEEEE HAPPIEST BIRTHDAY LOVEEEE..
I AM THANKFUL TO YOU FOR YOUR PRESENCE, I AM THANKFUL TO YOU FOR ALL YOUR SMILES, LAUGHTER AND HAPPINESS, Enough to brighten up my day making me feel alive, helping me stay positive and calm when it's hard to. Thanks for all your hardwork and still showing us the happiest face despite the fact that you do get tired, you do suffer but still you gave us the best of us. I am no stupid to write such long thing for no reason but i can right it for you,  My only reason to smile, TO LIVE. life has been cruel to me but it will not matter unless i got to see your smiling face at the end of the day. Nahh no hardship matters unless i see you working hard and still laughing, spreading positivity. THANKS FOR BEING AN HEALING OINTMENT. THANKS FOR BEING ARMY'S SEOKJINIE, MY HAPPINESS, A SMILING WORLD OF MINE. THANKS FOR MAkING ME FALL IN LOVE WITH YOU, WITH MYSELF. i love you and the letters are supposed to end and my words they're not enough to tell how precious you're. LOVE YOU, AGAIN A VERY HAPPY BIRTHDAY.

text: im hours away from leaving to my own military training and i am going to miss you, Bangtan. you came into my life during Wings era, when i needed you the most and for that, you hold a very Special place in my heart. this will be my last chance to say these things and i wish i could be more thorough but, in short... MEGA HAPPY BIRTHDAY JIN, may your day be full of support and unforgettable memories! Jimin to have seen your vocals, fluid dance and mental health blossom, has been a beautiful gift. Kookie, you have grown into such a mesmerizing artist of heartbreak vocals and i couldn't be more proud; your cover of BIGBANG's "If You" is a timeless Gem. Hobi, my heartâ™¡ you push yourself to your absolute Limits, all for your passion of dance and it is powerful. Jung Hoseok please know, i will never not be inspired by All that you are. Yoongi, your musical talents as a rapper, as a producer and sweetheart personality, you were meant for this life. i hope you continue to get the recognition. Tae, from growling your verses to stunning vocals, you are truly painted in your own color. just once, i'd like to see the world through your eyes. Joon you are a phenomenal leader and to see how your, already stellar, dance has improved. im grateful for how hard you work and everything you continue to do for the boys. which leads me back to you, Jin. i know you've cared for your brothers just as much. more than anything, the journey your vocals have taken is nothing short of moving and has genuinely brought me to tears, more than you can imagine. thank you all for your artistry, these past few years. for being my solace... thank you Bangtan, for being my Home. i love you, no. i purple you.
